enhanced_by.reason: The plus method modifies the current Pos instance, which can be used to prepare the state for the sum method.
The plusAll method aggregates multiple Pos instances, similar to the sum method, and can be used to prepare the state.
The equals method can be used to assert that the resulting Pos from the sum method matches the expected aggregated Pos.
The describeTo method can be used to generate a string representation of the Pos, which can be compared to the expected output of the sum method.
